\begin_layout Standard
## The Data:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The data for the chart "WhatsApp Extraordinary Growth in Users" seems to
 offer an inappropriate comparison.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
http://techcrunch.com/2014/02/19/facebook-whatsapp/?ncid=twittersocialshare
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In my opinion, WhatsApp user growth should be compared to rival messaging
 apps and not social media networks.
 Chart 3 reveals the growth rate of WeChat in China, the largest smart phone
 market.
 Did facebook acquire WhatsApp to become a hegemon for WeChat?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Chart 3: WhatsApp Extraordinary Growth in Users: the hegemon to WeChat?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Source: Business Insider
\end_layout

